<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 16:07:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登批准对俄罗斯实施500项新制裁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-on-russia-white-house/articleshow/107945137.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107945137.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登总统宣布因乌克兰战争和阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼之死对俄罗斯再实施 500 项制裁。美国将对近100家实体实施出口限制，并采取措施减少俄罗斯的能源收入。制裁将针对违反制裁者、俄罗斯金融部门、国防工业和采购网络。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 11:57:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-on-russia-white-house/articleshow/107945137.cms</guid></item><item><title>出售黑客：我们从中国大规模网络泄露中学到了什么</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/hackers-for-sale-what-weve-learned-from-chinas-massive-cyber-leak/articleshow/107947042.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107947042.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国网络安全公司 I-Soon 的大规模数据泄露让我们得以难得一睹与北京有关的黑客的内部运作。泄露的数据包括受影响的政府机构、电信服务提供商和高等教育机构。目标范围从邻国到国内地区和非法活动。客户包括警察部门和国家安全机构。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/hackers-for-sale-what-weve-learned-from-chinas-massive-cyber-leak/articleshow/107947042.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国监管机构从气候规则草案中删除了一些排放披露要求</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-regulator-drops-some-emissions-disclosure-requirements-from-draft-climate-rules/articleshow/107946091.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107946091.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 取消了对美国上市公司披露其企业气候风险规则中的范围 3 排放量的要求，这背离了欧盟的规则。这一决定可能会使跨国公司的合规性变得复杂，并对拜登总统的气候议程构成打击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:14:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-regulator-drops-some-emissions-disclosure-requirements-from-draft-climate-rules/articleshow/107946091.cms</guid></item><item><title>在埃塞俄比亚，一个秘密委员会下令杀戮和逮捕以镇压叛乱分子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/in-ethiopia-a-secret-committee-orders-killings-and-arrests-to-crush-rebels/articleshow/107945720.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107945720.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃塞俄比亚奥罗米亚地区的科里·纳吉尼亚委员会在总理阿比·艾哈迈德政府领导下运作，涉嫌侵犯人权，包括法外处决和非法拘留。该委员会的目标是镇压奥罗莫解放军并解决奥罗米亚的安全挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/in-ethiopia-a-secret-committee-orders-killings-and-arrests-to-crush-rebels/articleshow/107945720.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党称以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成两名护理人员和战斗人员死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-says-2-paramedics-fighter-dead-in-israeli-strike-on-lebanon/articleshow/107942505.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107942505.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据真主党和安全部门消息人士称，以色列对黎巴嫩南部一个村庄的袭击中，两名护理人员和一名真主党战士丧生。以色列军队证实，其袭击目标是黎巴嫩南部布利达的真主党“军事大院”。自10月7日以来，以色列和哈马斯之间的冲突几乎每天都会导致跨境交火。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-says-2-paramedics-fighter-dead-in-israeli-strike-on-lebanon/articleshow/107942505.cms</guid></item><item><title>加入伊斯兰国的英国出生女性因剥夺公民身份上诉失败</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-born-woman-who-joined-islamic-state-loses-appeal-over-citizenship-removal/articleshow/107942978.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107942978.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:44:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-born-woman-who-joined-islamic-state-loses-appeal-over-citizenship-removal/articleshow/107942978.cms</guid></item><item><title>“一切都在变得更糟”：疲劳标志着乌克兰战争周年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/everything-is-getting-worse-fatigue-marks-ukraine-war-anniversary/articleshow/107942660.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107942660.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:27:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/everything-is-getting-worse-fatigue-marks-ukraine-war-anniversary/articleshow/107942660.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争：加沙卫生部称死亡人数达到29,514人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-war-death-toll-touches-29514-says-health-ministry-in-gaza/articleshow/107941020.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107941020.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和哈马斯领导的巴勒斯坦领土武装战争中至少有 29,514 人死亡，自 2023 年 10 月 7 日战争开始以来已有 69,616 人受伤。内塔尼亚胡提出加沙“第二天”计划，主张通过直接谈判解决问题。呼吁加沙非军事化和去激进化。公众普遍同意取代哈马斯在加沙的统治。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-war-death-toll-touches-29514-says-health-ministry-in-gaza/articleshow/107941020.cms</guid></item><item><title>萨尔瓦多总统在华盛顿郊外的保守派聚会上受到摇滚明星般的欢迎</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/el-salvadors-president-nayib-bukele-receives-rock-star-welcome-at-conservative-gathering-outside-washington/articleshow/107941526.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107941526.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;萨尔瓦多总统纳伊布·布克莱在保守党政治行动会议上受到摇滚明星般的欢迎，他敦促人们与“黑暗势力”作斗争，并以萨尔瓦多作为警告。他强调了打击帮派、逮捕罪犯、罢免腐败法官的必要性，并强调了下一任美国总统能够识别和打击这些潜在力量的重要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/el-salvadors-president-nayib-bukele-receives-rock-star-welcome-at-conservative-gathering-outside-washington/articleshow/107941526.cms</guid></item><item><title>成千上万的乌克兰人在寻找失踪亲人时生活在痛苦和不确定之中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-of-ukrainians-in-agony-as-they-search-for-missing-loved-ones/articleshow/107940582.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940582.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于俄罗斯的入侵，乌克兰有数千人失踪。家人拼命寻找亲人，但缺乏官方信息让他们陷入困境。红十字国际委员会收集 DNA 样本以确定失踪人员的身份。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-of-ukrainians-in-agony-as-they-search-for-missing-loved-ones/articleshow/107940582.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦最高法院在强烈反对后捍卫对少数群体的裁决</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-supreme-court-defends-ruling-on-minorities-after-backlash/articleshow/107940868.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940868.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦最高法院为首席大法官卡齐·法兹·伊萨（Qazi Faez Isa）辩护，此前他因一项涉及亵渎罪的裁决而面临强烈反对和死亡威胁。这项裁决涉及释放艾哈迈迪教派的一名男子，该教派被一些强硬的穆斯林学者认为是异端。该男子被指控分享了一段被禁止的艾哈迈迪文本，这被视为亵渎。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-supreme-court-defends-ruling-on-minorities-after-backlash/articleshow/107940868.cms</guid></item><item><title>警方称瑞典约有 62,000 人与犯罪团伙有关联</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/62000-persons-linked-to-criminal-gangs-in-sweden-police/articleshow/107940485.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940485.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;瑞典约有 62,000 人活跃于犯罪网络或与犯罪网络有联系。过去十年，致命枪击事件增加了两倍多。 2022年，瑞典发生了62起致命枪击事件，是挪威、丹麦和芬兰三国枪击事件总和的九倍。爆炸袭击也创历史新高。 2021 年 9 月是瑞典自 2019 年以来死亡人数最多的一个月。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:22:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/62000-persons-linked-to-criminal-gangs-in-sweden-police/articleshow/107940485.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列对最大买家印度的军品出口未受加沙战争影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/israels-military-exports-to-top-buyer-india-unaffected-by-gaza-war/articleshow/107940247.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940247.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:11:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/israels-military-exports-to-top-buyer-india-unaffected-by-gaza-war/articleshow/107940247.cms</guid></item><item><title>奥地利前总理塞巴斯蒂安·库尔茨伪证案审判进入最后一天</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/austrian-ex-chancellor-sebastian-kurzs-perjury-trial-enters-final-day/articleshow/107940014.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107940014.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;奥地利前总理塞巴斯蒂安·库尔茨的伪证案审判即将结束。检察官指控他淡化了自己对 OBAG 任命的影响力。库尔兹否认有不当行为。他的政治前途和声誉受到威胁。公众舆论反对他重返领导岗位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 09:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/austrian-ex-chancellor-sebastian-kurzs-perjury-trial-enters-final-day/articleshow/107940014.cms</guid></item><item><title>弗拉基米尔·普京称俄罗斯95%的核力量已实现现代化</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vladimir-putin-says-95-of-russias-nuclear-forces-have-been-modernised/articleshow/107939248.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107939248.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vladimir-putin-says-95-of-russias-nuclear-forces-have-been-modernised/articleshow/107939248.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡公布了战后加沙计划的细节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-pm-netanyahus-plan-for-postwar-gaza-security-control-and-civilian-affairs/articleshow/107938169.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107938169.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:07:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-pm-netanyahus-plan-for-postwar-gaza-security-control-and-civilian-affairs/articleshow/107938169.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国医院延长工作时间应对医生抗议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-hospitals-extend-working-hours-to-tackle-doctors-protest/articleshow/107938029.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107938029.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-hospitals-extend-working-hours-to-tackle-doctors-protest/articleshow/107938029.cms</guid></item><item><title>受乌克兰鼓舞，俄罗斯庆祝爱国节日</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-marks-patriotic-holiday-amid-ukraine-offensive/articleshow/107936009.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107936009.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总统弗拉基米尔·普京在进攻两周年前夕赞扬了乌克兰的战士，承认他们为对抗弹药短缺的乌克兰军队所做的努力。普京的讲话是在莫斯科的“祖国保卫者日”爱国节日期间发表的，这个节日传统上展示了军事盛况和克里姆林宫支持的爱国主义。本周早些时候，他嘲笑乌克兰士兵从阿夫季夫卡“混乱地逃亡”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 07:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-marks-patriotic-holiday-amid-ukraine-offensive/articleshow/107936009.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普承诺捍卫基督教，反对左派，他说左派想要“推倒十字架”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-vows-to-protect-christianity-against-the-lefts-attempt-to-tear-down-crosses/articleshow/107935007.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107935007.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普在宗教广播公司大会上发表讲话时承诺保护基督教价值观，并警告左翼人士希望“拆除十字架”。他还表达了捍卫基督教信仰及其象征的承诺。特朗普在共和党初选中受到青睐，曾经拥挤的竞选场地现在只剩下他和他的前驻联合国大使尼基·黑利(Nikki Haley)。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 06:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-vows-to-protect-christianity-against-the-lefts-attempt-to-tear-down-crosses/articleshow/107935007.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国高速公路结冰 百车连环连环相撞 多人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/several-injured-in-100-car-pile-up-on-icy-china-expressway/articleshow/107936768.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107936768.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;因极端天气条件，苏州高速公路结冰，100多辆汽车相撞，多人受伤入院治疗。官方媒体、中央电视台和社交媒体的视频显示，汽车成群结队，玻璃和碎片散落各处。事故原因正在调查中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 07:24:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/several-injured-in-100-car-pile-up-on-icy-china-expressway/articleshow/107936768.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>